":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55d55272c15146582bbaa663a80836f2418e6eae","tid":1312701,"uid":269399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"556f7f558a6621dd5375d4205af4585d4fcd376f","tid":1312701,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"唔見咗出世紙同BNO<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"去差館報失，係香港補領出世紙，到你上網申請續領時，有個位係比你咁唔見左要續領，要警局報失紙，補領左的出世紙就彩色影印比佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"報失係指BNO?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"網上報失就OK<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/report-a-lost-or-stolen-passport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Freport-a-lost-or-stolen-passport&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=481ac924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/report-a-lost-or-stolen-passport</a>"},{"pid":"55a3de123da1f75ca9b3832b13af6d27ad092e52","tid":1312701,"uid":61281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"online apply完佢寫要寄咩就寄<br />\n我個人唔洗出世紙"},{"pid":"040570868adc5e8a0a5a595aaee4f9b37f96515d","tid":1312701,"uid":36034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"我個case<br />\n<br />\n十幾二十年前過左expiry，果時係bb相，之後搬屋果時唔見左本bno<br />\n<br />\n首先我大約六月中online report loss，之後佢叫我打電話去HM Office，第一次打去就refer左我去另一個hotline，之後第二次就話ok，等佢review再cancel passport，會有reference code比番我，等左兩星期都無，再打去吹一吹，當晚即刻出左code比我<br />\n<br />\n七月五號香港寄出 documents<br />\n七月十號HM Office收到<br />\n七月十號put into process queue<br />\n七月十五號approved<br />\n<br />\ndocuments list<br />\n1. 特區 colour copy<br />\n2. HKID colour copy<br />\n3. 副簽document<br />\n4. 公司employment letter (有名有地址)<br />\n5. 交稅張單(其實可以唔洗依份，我買多個保險，當地址用)<br />\n<br />\np.s. 由頭到尾佢個list都無叫我比出世紙，我朋友佢同我同期申請，佢本bno無唔見，反而佢要出世紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}